a.n: Exchange student 4: Tiffany Doll & Alec Knight

p.k: Ben's been kicked out of his house because of his affair with an exchange student, so imagine his surprise when his buddy Alex and his wife Dana are taking in an exchange student of their own. Old habits die hard as new passions are born, swirling around the sumptuous French student, Tiffany. A Sweet Sinner film.
